title: MONDAY - Week 14 recap: Chiefs #1 2020
itunes:title: MONDAY - Week 14 recap: Chiefs #1 2020
description:
Josh Allen and the Bills hand the Steelers their 2nd-straight loss (0:11) as Stefon Diggs reaches an elite milestone. The Chiefs move into the top-seed in the AFC (1:27) as they rally to beat the Dolphins. Despite the win, Patrick Mahomes not loving his trips to South Beach (1:54). In the NFC, The Packers clinch another NFC North crown (2:26) and Jalen Hurts (2:44) leads the Eagles to the upset win over the Saints
